author: COMSOL
description: This example of a geothermal doublet shows how to couple heat transfer and fluid flow for predicting the long term performance of a hydrothermal doublet system in a layered subsurface traversed by a fault zone. It includes modeling wells, fractures, and geologic layers with different hydraulic and thermal properties.
